title: Manchester United stars like Zlatan Ibrahimovic and Paul Pogba face pay cut if they fail to make Champions League
text:
EFL ZLAT'S GOTTA HURT Manchester United stars like Zlatan Ibrahimovic and Paul Pogba face pay cut if they fail to make Champions League 
Last season's flops were hit in the pocket after missing out - and this term's squad face could lose 25% of their wages Exclusive
